

in static variable types are known at stage of compiling and they can not change
in dynamic types of variable can change while program will be working

diamond problem : when both classes has one parent and it can make working of some methods complexier

polymorphism is need when we do not want to make a lot different functions for diff types of variables and wants simply make one method for diff types

abstract class has virtual methods and can be overrided from its subclasses

lambda expression - одноразовая функция